'''Azẹ̀''' yin azọnwanu he nọ yin zinzan nado kun tọjihun kavi nado whlú nusinnọ de. Azẹ̀ nọ saba yin yiyizan to tọjihun mẹ, e nọ yin bibasi po owhlẹ̀ po kavi ogan bosọ nọ do alọkọ. Azẹ̀ he nọ yin yiyizan to ''Kayaks'' nọ dite ganji bo nọ do nusannu to onu ṣigba e ma nọ do alọkọ tangan de. 
Mọdopolọ, otò voovo lẹ wẹ do Azẹ̀ wunmẹwunmẹ lẹ he ye do nọ kún tọjihun lẹ. To Aflika, otò pẹvi pẹvi lẹ kavi gbetato he tin tọtó lẹpo wẹ nọ zan azẹ̀ voovo lẹ.
